                                                      ;          2) Glyph Mode (64x40 text)
                                                      ;          3) 128x80 x 16-Color
1801                  GFX_AUX equ     $1801   ; (Byte) gfx auxillary/emulation flags:
                                                      ;      bit 7: 1:fullscreen / 0:windowed
                                                      ;      bit 6: reserved
                                                      ;      bit 5: reserved
                                                      ;      bit 4: reserved
                                                      ;      bit 3: reserved
                                                      ;      bit 0-2: monitor display index (0-7)
